GUSH.description: GUSH (also known as GUSHER) is one of Iowa City's most prolific writers and has full color throw ups seemingly everywhere around the city. I consider them one of if not THE best artist in the city. It's more common to find a huge spray painted tag than it is to find a handstyle! GUSH goes above and beyond by also putting 100% into repping their group TC/TCK (TOO COOL KRUE) with full color stylized lettering alongside every tag.
